3. Mission

Empower Holders â€“ Give all NFT owners, from BAYC whales to rug-pull survivors, a way to extract real value.

Balance Incentives â€“ Reward credible collections while still including unverified ones through proof-of-burn mechanics.

Deflationary Tokenomics â€“ Make CATA a sustainable asset through continuous burn mechanics and dynamic fees.

Governance for All â€“ Create a governance model that scales with the ecosystem, balancing top collections with small contributors.

Bridge Legitimacy â€“ Increase blue-chip acceptance by filtering junk responsibly without excluding survivors.

Secure by Design â€“ Establish a new security standard with DRS (7:5 guardian council), protecting deployer and admin keys from compromise.

